Package: daisyduck
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: a free player for Daisy 2.02 audio books
 DaisyDuck is a player for Daisy 2.02 DTB (Digital Talking Book).
 It provides the ability to play online books through the VideoLAN
 library.
